<li>Please forgive me for my mistakes. I value our relationship more than words can say.</li>
<li>I messed up, and I take full responsibility. I hope you can find it in your heart to forgive me.</li>
<li>I am truly sorry for causing you such distress. I’ll strive to do better.</li>
<li>I feel terrible about what happened.  My actions were wrong, and I regret them deeply.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for letting you down.  I love you, and I promise to earn back your trust.</li>
<li>Please accept my sincerest apologies.  I deeply regret my behavior.</li>
<li>I understand I hurt you, and for that I am truly sorry.</li>
<li>I own my mistakes and I am committed to making things right.</li>
<li>My actions were wrong, and I ask for your forgiveness.  I cherish our family bond.</li>
<li>I'm sorry for causing any pain or disappointment.  I value our relationship immensely.</li>
